# 
# CentOS 8 LedgerSMB Easy Installer
# 
# By: STEVE ARBOUR 	
# License: GNU GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE, Version 2, June 1991
# 
#################################################################################
# 
# STEP REQUIRED: 
#
# INSTALL CENTOS 8 - SERVER NO GUI
# UNPACK THIS INSTALLER
# READ THIS FILE FOR USAGE SYNTAX.
# EDIT THE FILE CONFIGURATION
# MAKE THE INSTALLER EXECUTABLE (chmod ug+x install.sh)
# MAKE USE OF THE INSTALLER (install.sh)
# 
# THIS SCRIPT REQUIRE:
#
# - AN EXTERNAL IP ADDRESS
# - A HOSTNAME THAT RESOLVE TO THAT IP ADDRESS
# - AN EMAIL ADDRESS FOR LETSENCRYPT TO USE.
#
# 
# Usage: install.sh <selinux_mode> <ipv6_mode> <ledgersmb_git_branch>
#
# Valid values for <selinux_mode> enforcing, permissive, disabled (Default is: enforcing)
# Valid values for <ipv6_mode> enabled, disabled (Default is: disabled)
# Valid values for <ledgersmb_git_branch> 1.7, master (Default is: master)
#
#
# Examples of use:
#
# Ex: './install.sh'
# (Would default install with selinux enforcing configured and ipv6 disabled.)
#
# Ex: './install.sh disabled enabled master'
# (Would install with selinux disabled and ipv6 enabled and ledgersmb lastest version.)
#
#################################################################################